{"title":"Manual SCHG 2021 Copy-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Manual SCHG 2021 Copy-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Manual SCHG\\N2021","guid":"w0DPsnbC2igntm4zNXK61Q","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Inmunocompromiso y\\NAparato Digestivo","guid":"E_Go7ipHixBlrcB5Z6a5Lg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Introducción","guid":"ez4r8V0QNJZzEc5_GReR2Q","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Aumento de trastornos\\NGI mediados por SI.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Inmunodeficiencias (ID) primarias y\\Nadquiridas → manifestaciones GI.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"• Inmunosupresión secundaria o adquirida\\N↔ terapias farmacológicas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"• Trasplantes de órganos\\Nsólidos (300/año en Chile).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"• Nuevas terapias\\Ninmunomoduladoras (10%-20%\\Npop.).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"2","text":"• Antineoplásicos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"2","text":"• ID primarias en\\Nadultos: SIgAD, CVID.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Concepto de Inmunosupresión y\\NFisiopatología del SI y Aparato Digestivo","guid":"b--IPDDwj6ZoEJT_YcUyHg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• SGI = gran superficie\\Npresentadora de Ag.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"• Modificación de respuesta ↔ estructuras adyacentes (esfínter),\\Nprocesos digestivos (ácidos, sales biliares, enzimas\\Npancreáticas), pH, tipo de alimento, nutrientes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"• Digestión y absorción → moléculas simples →\\Natraviesan pared GI → estimulación local y a\\Ndistancia ↔ complejo Ag/Ac.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"• Alteración de estos procesos → síndromes que\\Ncomprometen RI ↔ sistema digestivo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"1","text":"Concepto de Microbioma e\\NInmunosupresión","guid":"H67dOQrByIAl6emDVSv_lw","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• TGI humano ↔ red diversa de\\Nmicroorganismos = microbiota.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"• Papel importante en\\Nsalud y enfermedad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"• SI adaptado ↔ trabajo\\Nconjunto con microbiota.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"• Manipulación de microbiota →\\Nprevenir enfermedades.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"15","text":"• Alteración por\\Nantibióticos/inmunosupresores →\\Nvulnerabilidad ↔ enfermedades\\Nnosocomiales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"15","text":"• Microbiota:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"15","text":"• Bacteroidetes, Firmicutes,\\NActinobacteria, Proteobacteria.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"15","text":"• Bacteroidetes =\\N90% densidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"15","text":"• Cambios ↔ distribución anatómica → absorción de\\Nnutrientes, modificación de pH, producción de mucus,\\Npresentación de Ag a nivel celular.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"15","text":"• Desregulación ↔ cambios en microbioma (ej.:\\Nantibióticos, inmunosupresores).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"1","text":"Tipos de\\NInmunosupresión","guid":"UoMwvUue6YZrZNvsNEgUkA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Primarias","guid":"MOols0Sc58dlKEYLNUWZOw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Déficit selectivo de IgA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"• Inmunodeficiencia\\Ncomún variable","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"Adquiridas","guid":"IEmVMxoKVo4uLgelb9fj9Q","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Secundaria a fármacos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"•\\NQuimioterapia/radioterapia/corticoides","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"•\\NBiológicos/inmunosupresión/trasplante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"• Infecciosas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"30","text":"• HIV\\N(inmunodeficiencia\\Nadquirida)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"30","text":"• No VIH (micobacterias, estreptococos,\\Ncándida, parasitosis, chagas, VHB, VHC)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"30","text":"• Metabólicas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"30","text":"• Sd. Malabsorción","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"30","text":"• Déficit de oligoelementos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"30","text":"• DM2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"30","text":"• Enfermedades renales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"30","text":"• Enteropatía\\Nperdedora de\\Nproteínas","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"1","text":"Inmunodeficiencia Primaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Inmunodeficiencia Congénita","guid":"QigVqSnQTcxJZtWYPWZBmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"1","text":"I. Deficiencia Selectiva de\\NInmunoglobulina A (SIgAD)","guid":"BuCCYzx4pBdWfdN0dtAKnw","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• IgA: >70% de Ig\\Ntotales en el cuerpo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"• Baja concentración en suero ↔ secreciones mucosas\\N(nasal, pulmonar, saliva, lágrimas, leche materna,\\Nsecreciones urogenitales e intestinales).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"• Función: recubrimiento de\\Nmicroorganismos → prevención de\\Nfijación y penetración de patógenos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"• SIgAD:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"45","text":"• ID primaria más común.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"45","text":"• Definición: ausencia parcial/total de IgA en\\Nsuero (<0,07 g/L) en >4 años.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"45","text":"• Cifras normales en otras Ig.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"45","text":"• Etiología:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"45","text":"• Susceptibilidad\\Ngenética no bien\\Ndefinida.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"45","text":"• Herencia: autosómica\\Ndominante/recesiva en algunas\\Nfamilias.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"45","text":"• Casos esporádicos comunes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"45","text":"• Asociación: haplotipos HLA\\N(HLA-A1, B8, DR3).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"45","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"45","text":"• Mayoría asintomática.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"45","text":"• Posible compensación\\Npor otras Ig (ej.: IgG).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"45","text":"• Mayor riesgo de infecciones (ej.:\\NH. pylori, Giardia lamblia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"45","text":"• Autoinmunidad: mayor riesgo\\Nde enfermedad atópica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"45","text":"• Enfermedades autoinmunes\\Nprevalentes: lupus, enfermedad celíaca,\\Nenfermedad inflamatoria intestinal.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"1","text":"II. Inmunodeficiencia\\NComún Variable (IDCV)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Sistema inmune: complejo y altamente regulado para\\Nmantener homeostasis inmunológica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"• IDCV:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"• Trastorno sintomático más común\\Nen adultos con ID primarias.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"• Hipogammaglobulinemia\\Nnotable (sello distintivo).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"64","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"64","text":"• Heterogénea y variable.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"64","text":"• Bajo número de células plasmáticas y\\Nniveles disminuidos de Ig.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"64","text":"• Infecciones: bacterias en\\Ntractos respiratorio y GI.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"64","text":"• Trastornos\\Nautoinmunes a pesar de\\NID.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"64","text":"• Riesgos: neoplasias (especialmente\\Ndigestivas y hematológicas).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"64","text":"• Manifestaciones GI:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"64","text":"• Diarrea crónica,\\Nintermitente o persistente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"64","text":"• Esteatorrea, distensión abdominal,\\Npérdida de peso, déficit de minerales y\\Nvitaminas liposolubles.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"64","text":"• Infecciones GI.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"64","text":"• Enteropatía autoinmune (AIE).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"64","text":"• Granulomas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"64","text":"• Afectación hepática:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"64","text":"• Al menos 10% de\\Nlos pacientes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"64","text":"• Causas: infecciones, reacciones autoinmunes,\\Nlinfoproliferación y neoplasias, granulomas, infiltración de\\Ncélulas inflamatorias, obstrucción biliar intrahepática.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"64","text":"• Asociación fuerte con\\Nenteropatía linfocítica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"64","text":"• Papel patogénico del eje\\Nintestino-hígado.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"1","text":"Inmunodeficiencia Adquirida","guid":"bWkzvT6OaHNYlTy9DRgQ9w","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"1","text":"Infecciones en Pacientes\\NInmunosuprimidos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• Contexto: Uso de inmunosupresores,\\Nterapias oncológicas, corticosteroides,\\Nterapias biológicas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"• Riesgo: ↑Morbilidad,\\Npotencialmente letales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"• Revisión sistemática\\N(Stuck et al., 2016):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"87","text":"• RR: 1,6 (IC 95% 1,3-1,9).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"87","text":"• Dosis de corticoides ≤ 30 mg/día de prednisona:\\N9-58 eventos infecciosos/100 pacientes/año, ↑ en EII\\Nvs. patologías reumatológicas.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"1","text":"Fármacos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"• Corticoides:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"• Frecuencia:\\NInfecciones más\\Ncomunes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"• Manifestaciones digestivas: Dependientes de\\Ndosis, tiempo de uso, comorbilidades.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"93","text":"• Patógenos frecuentes: Candida albicans\\N(colonización orofaríngea, esofágica).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"1","text":"Patógenos Comunes (Tabla 2)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"• Bacterias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"• Enterobacterias:\\NITU, bacteriemias.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus: Bacteriemias,\\Ninfecciones de piel y tejidos blandos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"98","text":"• Streptococcus spp.: Bacteriemias,\\Ninfecciones de piel y tejidos blandos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"98","text":"• Salmonella spp.:\\NDiarrea, bacteriemia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"98","text":"• Legionella: Neumonía.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"98","text":"• Listeria monocytogenes: Bacteriemia,\\Nmeningitis, romboencefalitis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"98","text":"• Nocardia sp.: Neumonía,\\Nabscesos cerebrales y cutáneos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"98","text":"• Rhodococcus equi: Neumonía,\\Nabscesos, bacteriemia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"98","text":"• Mycobacterium\\Ntuberculosis:\\NTuberculosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"98","text":"• Clostridium difficile: Diarrea,\\Ncolitis pseudomembranosa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"98","text":"• Virus:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"98","text":"• Virus respiratorios: Neumonía.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"98","text":"• Citomegalovirus: Compromiso\\Ndigestivo, pulmonar, SNC.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"98","text":"• Herpes simplex: Infecciones\\Ndiseminadas, crónicas, hepatitis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"98","text":"• Varicela zoster: Herpes\\Nzóster, varicela diseminada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"98","text":"• Parvovirus B19:\\NPancitopenia, síntomas\\Nlúpicos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"98","text":"• Virus hepatitis B:\\NRiesgo de reactivación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"98","text":"• Hongos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"98","text":"• Candida spp.: Candidiasis\\Ncutánea, mucosa, sistémica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"98","text":"• Cryptococcus sp.:\\NSNC, pulmonar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"98","text":"• Pneumocystis\\Njiroveci: Neumonía.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"98","text":"• Aspergillus spp.:\\NAspergilosis pulmonar\\Ninvasora.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"98","text":"• Zygomycetes: Mucormicosis rino\\Ncraneofacial, pulmonar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"98","text":"• Parásitos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"98","text":"• Toxoplasma gondii: Toxoplasmosis\\N(SNC, coriorretinitis, neumonía).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"98","text":"• Protozoos intestinales: Cryptosporidium\\Nsp., Giardia intestinalis, Entamoeba\\Nhistolytica (diarrea, disentería).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"98","text":"• Nematodes: Strongyloides sp.\\N(compromiso intestinal, hiperinfestación).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"1","text":"Infecciones en\\NPacientes con\\NVIH-SIDA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"• Prevalencia: 71 mil\\Npersonas en Chile (2017).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"• Autopsias: 82% con lesiones digestivas,\\N38% con más de un sitio afectado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"• Principios diagnósticos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"• Síntomas y signos clínicos: Rara vez\\Ndiagnósticos por sí solos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"127","text":"• Maniobras no\\Ninvasivas: Preferidas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"127","text":"• Infecciones\\Nmúltiples:\\NFrecuentes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"127","text":"• Diagnóstico predictivo: Basado en\\Ngrado de inmunocompromiso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"127","text":"• Manifestaciones GI tardías: Parte de\\Ninfecciones sistémicas (CMV, M. avium).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"127","text":"• Neoplasias digestivas: Linfomas,\\Nsarcoma de Kaposi, carcinoma anal.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"1","text":"Manifestaciones Clínicas","guid":"SVAw9H5_JkBiRBCOejpWpw","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"1","text":"Neumonía","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• Agentes: Staphylococcus aureus,\\NLegionella, Pneumocystis jirovecii","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"• Bacteriemia, infecciones del SNC,\\Nartritis (Staphylococcus aureus).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"138","text":"• Neumonía, cuadros diseminados\\N(Legionella, Pneumocystis jirovecii).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"1","text":"Diarrea","guid":"","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Agentes: Enterobacterias, Salmonella\\Nspp., Clostridium difficile, Cryptosporidium\\Nsp., Giardia intestinalis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"• Diarrea asociada\\Na antibióticos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"• Enteropatía idiopática a HIV.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"143","text":"• Diarrea inducida por drogas (azatioprina,\\Nquimioterapias, ciclosporina A, metotrexato).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"1","text":"Herpes Zoster (HZ)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"• Agente: Virus de la\\Nvaricela-zoster (VZV).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"• HZ diseminado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"• HZ oftálmico.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"1","text":"Reactivación de Hepatitis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"• Agente: Virus de la\\Nhepatitis B (VHB).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"• Reactivación al retirar\\Nterapia inmunosupresora.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"1","text":"Infecciones Fúngicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"• Agentes: Candida spp., Cryptococcus sp.,\\NAspergillus spp., Zygomycetes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"• Candidiasis de piel,\\Nmucosas, sistémica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"158","text":"• Neumonía, aspergilosis\\Npulmonar invasora.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"• Mucormicosis rino\\Ncraneofacial o pulmonar.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"1","text":"Infecciones en Pacientes\\NInmunocomprometidos (por\\NVIH/SIDA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"1","text":"Diagnóstico y\\NTratamiento (Tablas 5 y\\N6)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"• Epstein Barr Virus (EBV):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Lengua.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación: Placas\\Nlinguales blanquecinas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico:\\NHistología,\\Nendoscopia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Antiviral.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"165","text":"• Herpes simplex (HSV):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Lengua.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación:\\NEsofagitis, úlceras\\Norales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: IFI\\N(inmunofluorescencia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Antiviral.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"165","text":"• Norovirus:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: I. Delgado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación:\\NVómitos, diarrea.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: PCR fecal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Soporte.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"165","text":"• CMV:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Oral, esófago,\\Nestómago, intestino.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación: Odinofagia, úlceras\\Nesofágicas, gástricas, intestinales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: PCR.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Ganciclovir 5 mg/kg cada\\N12 h por 2-3 semanas o foscarnet 90\\Nmg/kg por 2 semanas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"165","text":"• Candida:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Lengua, esófago.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación: Odinofagia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: Cultivo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Fluconazol 200-400 mg por\\N7-10 días vía oral, Itraconazol 200-400 mg\\Npor 14-21 días vía oral.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"165","text":"• Strongiloidiasis:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Cerebro,\\Nintestino, hígado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación: Diarrea,\\Nenfermedad sistémica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: Serología.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Ivermectina 200 µg/kg oral\\Nuna vez al día durante 1 a 2 días.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"165","text":"• Criptosporidiosis:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Intestino delgado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación:\\NDiarrea crónica severa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: IFI.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Autolimitada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"165","text":"• Microsporidiosis:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Tubo\\Ndigestivo, vía biliar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación: Diarrea,\\Ndolor abdominal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: Tinciones, IFI.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Albendazol 400 mg por vía oral\\Ndos veces día durante 3 semanas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"165","text":"• Salmonella:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Intestino.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación: Bacteriemia,\\Ngastroenteritis disentérica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: Cultivos\\N(hemocultivos y coprocultivos).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: ATB\\N(ciprofloxacino/cefadroxilo).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"165","text":"• Chlamydia trachomatis:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación: Colon, recto.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación: Linfogranuloma\\Nvenéreo, úlcera rectal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: Cultivo\\Ny hemocultivo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: ATB\\N(doxiciclina/azitromicina).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"165","text":"• Micobacterium:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"165","text":"• Ubicación:\\NDuodeno, I.\\NDelgado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"165","text":"• Manifestación: Diarrea,\\NSd. malabsorción.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"165","text":"• Diagnóstico: Hemocultivo,\\Ncoprocultivo, biopsias.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"165","text":"• Tratamiento: Claritromicina (500 mg c/12\\Nh) + Etambutol (15 mg/kg día) ± Rifabutina\\N(300 mg una vez al día).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"1","text":"Otras Complicaciones\\NAsociadas a VIH (Tabla 6)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"• Cáncer anal:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"221","text":"• Diagnóstico:\\NEndoscópico,\\Nhistológico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"221","text":"• Tratamiento: Quimioterapia,\\Nradioterapia, vacunación VPH.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"221","text":"• Enfermedad de Kaposi:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"221","text":"• Diagnóstico:\\NEndoscópico,\\Nhistológico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"221","text":"• Tratamiento:\\NQuimioterapia,\\Nradioterapia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"221","text":"• Colangiopatía por VIH:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"221","text":"• Diagnóstico: Colangio RNM,\\Necografía abdominal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"221","text":"• Tratamiento:\\NPapilotomía, stent.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"221","text":"• VHB - VHC:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"221","text":"• Diagnóstico:\\NSerologías en\\Nsangre.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"221","text":"• Tratamiento: Antiviral.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"1","text":"Causas Secundarias de Síndromes\\NDisabsortivos (Tabla 7)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"• Preentérico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"• Gastritis autoinmune.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"234","text":"• Hepatitis crónica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"234","text":"• Cirrosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"234","text":"• Obstrucción biliar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"234","text":"• Entéricas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"234","text":"• Inflamaciones.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"234","text":"• Enfermedad sistémica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"234","text":"• Disbiosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"234","text":"• Parasitosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"234","text":"• Posentéricas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"234","text":"• Bloqueo linfático.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"234","text":"• Hipertensión portal.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"0","text":"Síndromes Disabsortivos","guid":"YXatKF2t94hTPYcwM_nd5Q","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"Definición:","guid":"F2VjiRVC93MfUjPcU7pTNw","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"• Síndrome en el cual el proceso digestivo o absortivo\\Nno aprovecha varios principios alimentarios, a pesar de\\Nun consumo nutricional normal.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"251","parent":"248","text":"Causas Primarias:","guid":"JgoZdHmCJb9bntIwIbZlDQ","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"• Enteropatía por sensibilidad al\\Ngluten (Enfermedad celíaca).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"251","text":"• Daño en la mucosa intestinal por\\Nrespuesta inmunitaria al gluten.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"248","text":"Causas Secundarias (Tabla 7):","guid":"PfSNAysJU0koz7VdcrqSwA","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Preentéricas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"• Gastritis autoinmune.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"254","text":"• Hepatitis crónica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"254","text":"• Cirrosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"254","text":"• Obstrucción biliar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"254","text":"• Enfermedad pancreática.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"254","text":"• Entéricas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"254","text":"• Inflamaciones.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"254","text":"• Enfermedad sistémica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"254","text":"• Disminución de la\\Nsupresión absortiva.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"254","text":"• Disbiosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"254","text":"• Parasitosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"254","text":"• Posentéricas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"254","text":"• Bloqueo linfático.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"254","text":"• Hipertensión portal.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"270","parent":"248","text":"Manifestación Principal:","guid":"ej32mHdzlig1Kc39Pje3NQ","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"• Diarrea:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"270","text":"• Diarrea de predominio intestino delgado: Diarrea\\Nposprandial volumosa, pérdida de peso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"270","text":"• Diarrea de predominio intestino grueso\\N(“diarrea colítica”): Heces de pequeño\\Nvolumen, con o sin sangre o mucus.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"248","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"ZyJbKn7gydNZ2UUOB3oihg","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"• Histología: Biopsias de\\Nmucosa intestinal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"274","text":"• Serología: Anticuerpos\\Nanti-transglutaminasa tisular,\\Nanti-endomisio.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"277","parent":"248","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"ebZ5AkYVH_th-v9VVg1QLw","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"• Primaria\\N(Enfermedad\\Ncelíaca):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"277","text":"• Dieta libre de gluten.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"277","text":"• Secundarias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"277","text":"• Preentéricas: Tratamiento de la\\Ncausa subyacente (gastritis\\Nautoinmune, hepatitis crónica, etc.).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"277","text":"• Entéricas: Tratamiento de inflamaciones, corrección\\Nde disbiosis, eliminación de parasitosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"277","text":"• Posentéricas: Tratamiento de bloqueo\\Nlinfático, control de hipertensión portal.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"0","text":"ENFERMEDAD POR REFLUJO\\NGASTROESOFÁGICO (ERGE)","guid":"KUzhDj6iYxxoQfJ1PT6J_A","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"Definición:","guid":"M6hsdRQeuZZbhGM1H4g6BA","children":[{"id":"286","parent":"285","text":"• RGE: Paso de contenido gástrico al esófago (fenómeno fisiológico).","guid":"PRVq1ztJe1s_YkhYXQBbGg","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"285","text":"• ERGE: Presencia de síntomas cardinales (pirosis, regurgitación, dolor torácico no coronario) y/o complicaciones específicas\\N(esofagitis, estenosis péptica, esófago de Barrett) debido a excesiva exposición esofágica al contenido gástrico.","guid":"bZpcayznyjxkDaaHHswHTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"288","parent":"284","text":"Factores de Riesgo:","guid":"Q0f33iKkLskzo5mzWq1bZw","children":[{"id":"289","parent":"288","text":"1. Índice de Masa\\NCorporal (IMC):","guid":"BtslqhDZxOoOT5F-Q_CQgQ","children":[{"id":"290","parent":"289","text":"• Asociación: ↑IMC → ↑riesgo de ERGE.","guid":"BaWD-CPGqCVVEgMxGPiD_Q","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"289","text":"• Metaanálisis\\N(22 estudios):","guid":"FK2lE0nB_49ENf0SBvdQxw","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"• Obesos: 22,1% prevalencia.","guid":"JNB_hm-OSVZiem2HReMRbw","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"291","text":"• No obesos: 14, 2% prevalencia.","guid":"MT0bRjjGqKZvTBtJZC-Nfg","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"291","text":"• OR: 1,73.","guid":"ZJoU_FkLPY07-wKlbp4iuw","children":[]}]},{"id":"295","parent":"289","text":"• Mecanismos:","guid":"E1MABXHCzzd79La_aXehsA","children":[{"id":"296","parent":"295","text":"• ↑Presión intraabdominal.","guid":"Vs07SE1whwNWINCdWxdtxQ","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"295","text":"• ↑Prevalencia de hernia hiatal.","guid":"E2lMzVThigpVmhr_Nxy4FA","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"295","text":"• ↑Gradiente de presión abdominal vs. torácica.","guid":"SvO_cQjYmp0emrZTX6FkhQ","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"295","text":"• ↑Niveles de estrógenos.","guid":"UpqaLGLQs2VmmLVMd2sZsg","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"295","text":"• ↑Producción de enzimas biliares y pancreáticas.","guid":"Ul78vEkTItM9TisiA5wYAg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"301","parent":"288","text":"2. Tabaquismo:","guid":"TCNARk2x2dYg8OubOb2csQ","children":[{"id":"302","parent":"301","text":"• Asociación: Fumadores → ↑prevalencia de ERGE.","guid":"AdnLeSyaRmtny6WAZnPgdQ","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"301","text":"• Metaanálisis\\N(30 estudios):","guid":"JeDWBgeX_ChYB6RMeHtwMg","children":[{"id":"304","parent":"303","text":"• Fumadores: 19, 6% prevalencia.","guid":"FYl3XVEGufACcCWubFaypQ","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"303","text":"• No fumadores: 15, 9% prevalencia.","guid":"HndA81iQ9ktHbiBqMeCNwQ","children":[]},{"id":"306","parent":"303","text":"• OR: 1,26.","guid":"LXKAVh0IO2lo_UXVeGY_xw","children":[]}]},{"id":"307","parent":"301","text":"• Mecanismos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"308","parent":"307","text":"• Prolonga el tiempo de eliminación del ácido esofágico.","guid":"amivjj6gWZhv5onlPMesSg","children":[]},{"id":"309","parent":"307","text":"• ↓Presión en el esfínter esofágico inferior.","guid":"B7N8bC00tQdAY8RMCY1H5Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"310","parent":"288","text":"3. Predisposición\\NGenética:","guid":"d5OmnCI9zzBwmq1eWqsoXw","children":[{"id":"311","parent":"310","text":"• Estudios en gemelos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"312","parent":"311","text":"• Herencia: 31%-43% de la predisposición a ERGE.","guid":"Wc77cigvacxwAShbX3R_ag","children":[]}]},{"id":"313","parent":"310","text":"• Factores de riesgo genéticos: Aún no se identifica locus específico.","guid":"S_YR8UUTK4x4bQNnYX-JTg","children":[]}]},{"id":"314","parent":"288","text":"4. Infección por Helicobacter pylori\\N(puede disminuir riesgo).","guid":"epmkEgT-kiJYiaP-buA1QQ","children":[{"id":"315","parent":"314","text":"• Asociación sugerida:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"316","parent":"315","text":"• H. pylori → Atrofia de la mucosa gástrica → ↓Producción de ácido.","guid":"FhnlfHrdKRVN1jv0NJEmbw","children":[]}]},{"id":"317","parent":"314","text":"• Metaanálisis (27 estudios):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"318","parent":"317","text":"• Erradicación de H. pylori: ↑Riesgo de esofagitis por reflujo.","guid":"U24fYRVEXF5mcbQwAOCftw","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"317","text":"• RR: 1,46.","guid":"MkyXyE9u-gV5Rt9-WC1tzg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"284","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"aOnuLU3vsu8k5UMqKxID1g","children":[{"id":"321","parent":"320","text":"Prevalencia Global:","guid":"YxeBw0qpn0VC1st_Z7iooQ","children":[{"id":"322","parent":"321","text":"• Prevalencia elevada y en aumento (especialmente en países industrializados).","guid":"N_-gejOVYqcIqXAyEDKHyg","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"321","text":"• Oscila entre 2,5% (China) y 51,2% (Grecia).","guid":"A1KGRBvc3zIvQp9_RCU8QQ","children":[]},{"id":"324","parent":"321","text":"• Rango de prevalencia: Influenciado por diferencias reales y metodológicas (algunos estudios consideran solo síntomas, otros esofagitis erosiva).","guid":"FoSNQh8_xmt0fPWFEheKgA","children":[]}]},{"id":"325","parent":"320","text":"Complicaciones:","guid":"JyN2jiN7WOYvocdeJkF8oA","children":[{"id":"326","parent":"325","text":"• Esofagitis erosiva y adenocarcinoma esofágico: Más frecuentes en personas de raza blanca con obesidad central.","guid":"djh6vV26pXx3UXv6OLvSZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"327","parent":"320","text":"Metaanálisis Reciente (79\\Nestudios en 36 países):","guid":"N8OAAFI4QYJdRqjuHwF0qQ","children":[{"id":"328","parent":"327","text":"• Prevalencia global (ERGE definida por síntomas): 13,3%.","guid":"Q8qS-R6bb6wWg3_xXLf-0g","children":[]},{"id":"329","parent":"327","text":"• Regiones con tasas\\Nsuperiores a la media:","guid":"ckmrs1sOf_crWExEW4McwA","children":[{"id":"330","parent":"329","text":"• Sur de Asia.","guid":"IRKR6UGu0e9WTDseKWkJ2Q","children":[]},{"id":"331","parent":"329","text":"• América Central.","guid":"MvJyOCvTbFZpvyJEV8t1Jw","children":[]},{"id":"332","parent":"329","text":"• América del Sur.","guid":"CgQNvzpHwng1x8ySDVaUAw","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"329","text":"• Europa.","guid":"ViShq2UKbBFRe9BEbKku7Q","children":[]},{"id":"334","parent":"329","text":"• América del Norte.","guid":"BEoyfEX4xcp-wLlteoKtOg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"335","parent":"320","text":"Variación con la Edad:","guid":"IzZqRHI9FO1St1yhfjsT1Q","children":[{"id":"336","parent":"335","text":"• < 50 años: 14,0%.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"337","parent":"335","text":"• > 50 años: 17,3%\\N(OR de 1,32).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"338","parent":"320","text":"Impacto:","guid":"THfzTgoGgM5_p6S9CmyAUg","children":[{"id":"339","parent":"338","text":"• Disminución de la calidad de vida.","guid":"OSNUeyUh5NpLVD7-UUZIFA","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"338","text":"• Altos costos sanitarios.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"341","parent":"320","text":"Mortalidad:","guid":"ATOLxE0p7T000-ZnRXFlpQ","children":[{"id":"342","parent":"341","text":"• No hay aumento de mortalidad global por todas las causas o específica por cáncer en pacientes con síntomas de ERGE.","guid":"I7NrRnYSNWczPn-eZ33-Pw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"343","parent":"284","text":"Manifestaciones\\NClínicas:","guid":"NQ_UFyh3Whp9JxMSL03Krw","children":[{"id":"344","parent":"343","text":"• Síntomas Cardinales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"345","parent":"344","text":"• Pirosis.","guid":"MTGq4kdexvIOh23zKugj5A","children":[]},{"id":"346","parent":"344","text":"• Regurgitación.","guid":"DXPm7XCCbUgA9XQTQRxTYw","children":[]},{"id":"347","parent":"344","text":"• Dolor torácico no coronario.","guid":"BKEm3lx510hgpI1nR-kevA","children":[]}]},{"id":"348","parent":"343","text":"• Complicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"349","parent":"348","text":"• Esofagitis.","guid":"fx4GEhRIJxoilnokNwUsTg","children":[]},{"id":"350","parent":"348","text":"• Estenosis péptica.","guid":"Zz30qVD-KMIU9mv_M7Xn9w","children":[]},{"id":"351","parent":"348","text":"• Esófago de Barrett.","guid":"WwSpkRSeELw-ImhJEBR9qA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"352","parent":"284","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"H-rwQzJQ4Q9thYHkBw1LbQ","children":[{"id":"353","parent":"352","text":"• Clínico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"354","parent":"353","text":"• Basado en síntomas cardinales.","guid":"QNK1_Xqnrg9v_SbsMFe5RA","children":[]}]},{"id":"355","parent":"352","text":"• Endoscopia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"356","parent":"355","text":"• Visualización de esofagitis, estenosis péptica, esófago de Barrett.","guid":"e5L9Plb4tFJpPa_3ZTnxeg","children":[]}]},{"id":"357","parent":"352","text":"• pH-metría esofágica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"358","parent":"357","text":"• Confirmación de exposición ácida excesiva.","guid":"QoNXpmYP7XwnSfOyXcetjQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"359","parent":"284","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"dEaRL3KVFHpJtCsyAbp4HA","children":[{"id":"360","parent":"359","text":"• Medidas Generales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"361","parent":"360","text":"• Modificación de estilo de vida (↓ peso, evitar tabaquismo, dieta).","guid":"GO1r2VOuPAdEiwAGTqBNcg","children":[]}]},{"id":"362","parent":"359","text":"• Farmacológico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"363","parent":"362","text":"• Inhibidores de la bomba de protones (IBP).","guid":"aTlxDUYEEfEWVoWreskeXg","children":[]},{"id":"364","parent":"362","text":"• Antagonistas de los receptores H2.","guid":"CFZ38HFDoEhVhzE3QFYYag","children":[]}]},{"id":"365","parent":"359","text":"• Quirúrgico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"366","parent":"365","text":"• Funduplicatura (en casos refractarios o complicaciones).","guid":"JNkC714woWlQiKA0XfxXag","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"367","parent":"284","text":"Fisiopatología\\Nde la ERGE","guid":"KsS82T72GOR1cI29GC3wlg","children":[{"id":"368","parent":"367","text":"1. Inicio del Proceso:","guid":"bOdudjNxeN1CY9EBFArlBA","children":[{"id":"369","parent":"368","text":"• Ascenso del contenido gástrico →\\NCascada de eventos epiteliales.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"370","parent":"367","text":"2. Mecanismo del Reflujo:","guid":"VuzRxHIFmF86TGGkDrBRxA","children":[{"id":"371","parent":"370","text":"• Presión intragástrica >\\Npresión intraesofágica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"372","parent":"370","text":"• ERGE: Alteración de la función de\\Nbarrera de la unión esofagogástrica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"373","parent":"370","text":"• Pérdida de la función efectiva del\\Nesfínter esofágico inferior (EEI).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"374","parent":"367","text":"3. Relajaciones\\NTransitorias del EEI:","guid":"RD3Z4ReTCpItscZuZ3REJQ","children":[{"id":"375","parent":"374","text":"• Fisiología: Respuesta normal a\\Nla distensión gástrica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"376","parent":"374","text":"• Facilitan eructos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"377","parent":"374","text":"• Patología: Contribuyen a ERGE si son\\Nfrecuentes y prolongadas.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"378","parent":"367","text":"4. Hernia Hiatal por\\NDeslizamiento:","guid":"CdAfgABpIw9lr1f7EKtFKg","children":[{"id":"379","parent":"378","text":"• Configuración\\Nanatómica común:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"380","parent":"378","text":"• Facilita el reflujo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"381","parent":"378","text":"• Aumenta la angulación entre la unión\\Ngastroesofágica y el fondo gástrico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"382","parent":"378","text":"• Reduce la función\\Nde la válvula.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"383","parent":"367","text":"5. Impacto del Reflujo\\Nen el Esófago:","guid":"EULn-XP-6XlUm9WrXWYoPw","children":[{"id":"384","parent":"383","text":"• Dependencia de los\\Nmecanismos de depuración:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"385","parent":"383","text":"• Peristalsis adecuada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"386","parent":"383","text":"• Factores defensivos: Saliva.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"387","parent":"383","text":"• Integridad epitelial:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"388","parent":"383","text":"• Proteínas de adhesión.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"389","parent":"383","text":"• Integridad de los\\Nespacios intercelulares.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"390","parent":"367","text":"6. Evidencia Reciente:","guid":"QbDDT3WMwUYXI8TwPEpnYQ","children":[{"id":"391","parent":"390","text":"• Duda sobre el paradigma\\Ntradicional de daño directo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"392","parent":"390","text":"• Daño epitelial\\Nmediado por linfocitos\\NT.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"393","parent":"284","text":"Presentación\\NClínica de la ERGE","guid":"fYSBWE4FynslRgGNRtSyTA","children":[{"id":"394","parent":"393","text":"1. Síntomas:","guid":"eotTaG-taO8rKpyjch76BA","children":[{"id":"395","parent":"394","text":"• Cardinales:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"396","parent":"394","text":"• Pirosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"397","parent":"394","text":"• Regurgitación ácida.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"398","parent":"394","text":"• Dolor torácico no coronario.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"399","parent":"394","text":"• Atípicos y Extraesofágicos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"400","parent":"394","text":"• Otorrinolaringológicos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"401","parent":"394","text":"• Tos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"402","parent":"394","text":"• Laringitis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"403","parent":"394","text":"• Descarga posterior.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"404","parent":"394","text":"• Broncopulmonares.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"405","parent":"394","text":"• Orales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"406","parent":"394","text":"• Hipótesis: Vías neuronales compartidas o\\Nexposición de cuerdas vocales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"407","parent":"394","text":"• Pruebas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"408","parent":"394","text":"• Pruebas de reflujo esofágico:\\NPueden carecer de sensibilidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"409","parent":"394","text":"• Ensayos de respuesta a tratamiento\\Nmédico/quirúrgico: Limitados y resultados mixtos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"410","parent":"394","text":"• Ensayos aleatorizados con IBP: Negativos o\\Ndébilmente positivos en ciertas poblaciones.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"411","parent":"393","text":"2. Complicaciones:","guid":"ZLz30GKFrNUs5anKbo0XUA","children":[{"id":"412","parent":"411","text":"• Esofagitis:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"413","parent":"411","text":"• Inflamación de la mucosa\\Ndel esófago distal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"414","parent":"411","text":"• Erosiones.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"415","parent":"411","text":"• Prevalencia: 18%-25% en\\Npacientes sintomáticos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"416","parent":"411","text":"• Clasificación de Los Ángeles:\\NGrados A-D (de leve a severo).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"417","parent":"411","text":"• Estenosis Péptica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"418","parent":"411","text":"• Cicatrización fibrótica por\\Nexposición ácida.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"419","parent":"411","text":"• Incidencia: 7%-23% en pacientes con\\Nesofagitis erosiva no tratada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"420","parent":"411","text":"• Síntoma principal: Disfagia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"421","parent":"411","text":"• Tratamiento: IBP a largo plazo +\\Ndilatación endoscópica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"422","parent":"411","text":"• Esófago de Barrett:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"423","parent":"411","text":"• Metaplasia columnar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"424","parent":"411","text":"• Prevalencia: 7,2% en\\Npacientes con ERGE.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"425","parent":"411","text":"• Displasia: 13,9%,\\Nprincipalmente de bajo\\Ngrado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"426","parent":"411","text":"• Riesgo de adenocarcinoma:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"427","parent":"411","text":"• Sin displasia: Bajo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"428","parent":"411","text":"• Con displasia de bajo\\Ngrado: 0,54% anual.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"429","parent":"411","text":"• Con displasia de alto\\Ngrado: 1,73% anual.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"430","parent":"411","text":"• Vigilancia\\Nendoscópica\\Nrecomendada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"431","parent":"411","text":"• Adenocarcinoma Esofágico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"432","parent":"411","text":"• Incidencia en\\Naumento en occidente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"433","parent":"411","text":"• Riesgo relativo aumentado en\\Npacientes con ERGE.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"434","parent":"411","text":"• Riesgo absoluto bajo.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"435","parent":"284","text":"Historia Clínica:","guid":"Yu7P5BKVAcV_OFx6dDG33Q","children":[{"id":"436","parent":"435","text":"• Identificación de\\Ndiagnósticos diferenciales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"437","parent":"435","text":"• Descartar patología cardíaca en dolor\\Ntorácico antes de pruebas terapéuticas\\No estudios profundos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"438","parent":"284","text":"Diagnóstico Presuntivo y\\NPrueba Terapéutica:","guid":"bcQc7T6bFlIhL6G1R5MYXw","children":[{"id":"439","parent":"438","text":"• Pirosis y/o regurgitación ácida:\\NDiagnóstico presuntivo de ERGE.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"440","parent":"438","text":"• Prueba terapéutica con IBP si no hay\\Nsignos de alarma digestivos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"441","parent":"284","text":"Pruebas Diagnósticas:","guid":"ZsqAHhEwyhAnB5fJMsCSDw","children":[{"id":"442","parent":"441","text":"• Endoscopia: Indicado si no\\Nhay respuesta a IBP.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"443","parent":"441","text":"• Manometría esofágica de alta\\Nresolución: Evaluación de la motilidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"444","parent":"441","text":"• Monitoreo del pH esofágico: Evaluación del\\Ntiempo de exposición al ácido.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"445","parent":"284","text":"Criterios\\NDiagnósticos de\\NERGE:","guid":"VkP1nB90mzAUQBtebF3bGA","children":[{"id":"446","parent":"445","text":"• Endoscopia: Esofagitis\\Ngrado C o D, esófago de\\NBarrett, estenosis péptica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"447","parent":"445","text":"• Monitoreo de\\Nreflujo sin IBP:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"448","parent":"445","text":"• Tiempo de exposición al ácido\\N>6%: Diagnóstico de ERGE.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"449","parent":"445","text":"• Tiempo de exposición al ácido <4% o\\N<40 episodios de reflujo en 24h:\\NSugiere ausencia de ERGE.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"450","parent":"284","text":"Importancia del\\NDiagnóstico Preciso:","guid":"GlHERmIWV1Ig7wGHbb_jpw","children":[{"id":"451","parent":"450","text":"• Evitar pérdida de\\Ntiempo y recursos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"452","parent":"450","text":"• Prevenir insistencia en estrategias no basadas\\Nen evidencia (ej. aumento excesivo de dosis de\\NIBP, endoscopias repetidas).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"453","parent":"284","text":"Algoritmo 1. Acercamiento\\NDiagnóstico en la ERGE:","guid":"d1qzsAdgtbhuoINeKadLeA","children":[{"id":"454","parent":"453","text":"1. Historia\\Nclínica\\Ndetallada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"455","parent":"453","text":"2. Descartar patología\\Ncardíaca en dolor torácico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"456","parent":"453","text":"3. Prueba terapéutica con IBP en\\Nausencia de signos de alarma.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"457","parent":"453","text":"4. Endoscopia si no hay\\Nrespuesta a IBP.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"458","parent":"453","text":"5. Manometría esofágica y monitoreo\\Nde pH si persisten síntomas.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":458,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Manual SCHG 2021 Copy-2024-1","id":"map_812","resolved_references":[]}